title: Harris' INT return leads Broncos to 16-10 win over Raiders
text:
> Sports Harris' INT return leads Broncos to 16-10 win over Raiders Oakland Raiders kicker Sebastian Janikowski (11) reacts with long snapper Jon Condo (59) after kicking a point after try during the first half of an NFL football game against the Denver Broncos in Oakland, Calif., Sunday, Oct. 11, 2015. Janikowski set the franchise record for games played with No. 241 against Denver. (AP Photo/Ben Margot) The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
